message.text: Actions job or workflow does not limit the permissions of the GITHUB_TOKEN. Consider setting an explicit permissions block, using the following as a minimal starting point: {{contents: read}}

steps.name: Install dependencies
steps.run: npm ci

steps.name: Rebuild the dist/ directory
steps.run:
npm run build
npm run pack

steps.name: Compare the expected and actual dist/ directories
steps.run:
if [ "$(git diff --ignore-space-at-eol dist/ | wc -l)" -gt "0" ]; then
  echo "Detected uncommitted changes after build.  See status below:"
  git diff
  exit 1
fi
